---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ProjectPage from "../../../components/ProjectPage.astro";
---
<Layout title="Modern ISE Website — Bence R.">
  <ProjectPage
    name="Modern ISE Website"
    date="December 2024"
    tags={["Next.js", "React", "Tailwind CSS", "Turso", "Prisma"]}
    image="/modern-ise-website.png"
    imageAlt="Modern ISE website screenshot"
    github="https://github.com/bencered/modern-ise-website"
    link="https://modern-ise-website.vercel.app"
  >
    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-heading">What?</h2>
      <p>A weekend exercise stepping outside my design comfort zone — a radical redesign of software-engineering.ie. The seed of the idea was wanting to make a site with square buttons. I'm most proud of the text animations. (Refresh the page.)</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-top:1.5rem">Why?</h2>
      <p>Practice design skills, try an industrial aesthetic, and propose a potential new direction for the official site.</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-top:1.5rem">Learnings</h2>
      <p>Design is fun. Square buttons look good.</p>
    </div>
  </ProjectPage>
</Layout>
